Subject: [PATCH] Route non-emergency tiles to info-form and remove redundant
 fields

Add dedicated non-emergency intake screen that only collects service type
and priority, then hands off to info-form which now receives those params,
displays them as read-only context, and submits them alongside its fields.

Co-Authored-By: Kyle Henry <kylehenry7000@gmail.com>
